OASISFormat: 0.3
Name: otfm
Version: %%VERSION%%
Synopsis: OpenType font decoder for OCaml
Authors: Daniel Bünzli <daniel.buenzli at erratique.ch>
Copyrights: (c) 2013 Daniel C. Bünzli
License: BSD3
Homepage: http://erratique.ch/software/otfm
Description:
 Otfm is an in-memory decoder for the OpenType font data format. It
 provides low-level access to tables of OpenType fonts and functions
 to decode some of them.
 
 Otfm is made of a single module and is distributed under a BSD
 license.

OCamlVersion: >= 4.00.0
Plugins: META (0.3)
